Examples 

Create 4 different integers 

int x;
int s;
int c;
int d;


a = 4;
b = 3;
c = 6;
d = 7;

Add all the integers

System.out.println(x+s+c+d);

Add two integers x and d

System.out.println(x+d);

subtract s and c

System.out.println(s-c);

Subtract all 

System.out.println(x-s-c-d);

multiply c by x

System.out.println(c * x);

Multiply  all?


Divide x by d

System.out.println(x / d);

Show the reminder of c to x

System.out.println(c%x); % module

Show the reminder of d to c?

